quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,60,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo Musa yabwiraga umukozi we ati \"Sinzigera mpagarika urugendo ntageze ku masangano y’inyanja ebyiri cyangwa nkagenda imyaka n’imyaniko\" (kugeza mpuye n’uwo nshaka)"
  18,61,"Nuko bageze ku masangano yazo, bahibagirirwa isamaki yabo maze (ya samaki ihinduka nzima) yifatira inzira yo mu nyanja"
  18,62,"Nuko ubwo bari bamaze kuharenga, (Musa) abwira umukozi we ati \"Tuzanire ifunguro ryacu ryo ku manywa, rwose twahuye n’umunaniro muri uru rugendo rwacu"
  18,63,"(Umukozi we) aramubwira ati \"Uribuka ubwo twaruhukiraga ku rutare? Mu by’ukuri, ni ho nibagiriwe (ku kubwira ibya) ya samaki kandi nta wundi wabinyibagije utari Shitani. Yafashe inzira y’inyanja mu buryo butangaje cyane"
  18,64,"(Musa) aravuga ati \"Aho (byabereye) ni ho twashakaga\". Nuko basubira inyuma bagana iyo baturutse (kuri rwa rutare)"
  18,65,"Nuko bahasanga umwe mu bagaragu bacu (Al Khidri) twahundagajeho impuhwe ziduturutseho, kandi twigishije ubumenyi budukomokaho"
  18,66,"Musa aramubwira ati \"Ese ngukurikire kugira ngo unyigishe bimwe mu byo wigishijwe bijyanye no kuyoboka"
  18,67,"(Al Khidri) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, ntuzigera ushobora kunyihanganira (kubera ibyo uzabona nkora)"
  18,68,Ubundi se ni gute wakwihanganira ibyo utigeze umenya
  18,69,"(Musa) aravuga ati \"Allah nabishaka uzasanga nihangana, kandi sinzigera nigomeka ku mabwiriza yawe"
  18,70,"(Al Khidri) aravuga ati \"Niba rero uhisemo kunkurikira, ntugire icyo umbaza kugeza igihe nza kugira icyo nkikubwiraho"